objectives.en:
1) to give an overview about learning in STEM education, based on constructivist learning theories;
2) to explain the development of conceptions and misconceptions in science education;
3) to give an overview about students appreciation of the nature of science.

learning_outcomes.en:
1) conceptualises learning in STEM education based on constructivist learning theories;
2) is able to explain the development of conceptions and misconceptions in science education;
3) is able to distinguish nature of science from science education.

learning_outcomes.et:
Õpiväljundid:
1) saab aru kontseptuaalsest õppimisest loodus- ja reaalainetes tuginedes konstruktivistlikele õpikäsitlustele;
2) oskab selgitada teaduslike arusaamade kujunemist ja väärarusaamade tekkimise põhjusi valdkondlike õppeainete näitel;
3) oskab eristada kooli õppeainet teadusest.
